{"tid":189722,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"蘭花系啤梨唔撚玩了 笑鳩義士摺埋現代豪俠傳","createTime":"2017-04-06T15:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T15:01:02.000Z","uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1510c3becbc78ee5c73ef9f74657f15da9521d","tid":189722,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T15:37:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0zBPhDanPhQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0zBPhDanPhQ&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=49d0159b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0zBPhDanPhQ</a><br />\n<br />\n所以話跟過人民力量 心態價值觀一世都會受到影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊年講到點樣支持後生仔 轉個頭都係屌鳩你哋死蠢 順便幫教主擦鞋算<br />\n<br />\n最撚興就係講到自己俾人恐嚇就好撚大付出<br />\n屌鳩你咩 你估班義士冇俾人跟？冚家都俾人跟啊屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又話如果知道警察開槍就冇人敢出來<br />\n係撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大把人開咗槍先飛的出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一開頭認自己冇膽淆底咪算囉</span>"},{"pid":"08795fd7f65420ebd285eebd2a85d6fac26a6c60","tid":189722,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117064f48b752d4c3e82276fd2b171f31e38b31b","tid":189722,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:53:25.000Z","msg":"俾人恐嚇?<br />\n<br />\n我試過有一部電話比情報科勾線tim啦<br />\n<br />\n係電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 柒黑警, 怕乜撚"},{"pid":"3a88e4ffb0b64e297a4898cd820ae330d30bef84","tid":189722,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾人恐嚇?<br />\n<br />\n我試過有一部電話比情報科勾線tim啦<br />\n<br />\n係電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 柒黑警, 怕乜撚</blockquote><br />\n條友冇膽扮大膽就不嬲架啦<br />